[100, -50, 200, null, 50] >> transactions.

"--- Aggregating Totals ---" >> Display.

transactions >> Filter:
    @ >> item.
    item >> Type >> check:
        is "list": false >> Return.
    ..
    item >> check:
        is < 0: false >> Return.
    ..
    true >> Return.
.. >> valid_tx.

valid_tx >> Reduce:
    (@[0] & @[1]) >> Add >> Return.
.. >> total.

"Total: " >> msg.
(total >> Str) >+> msg.
msg >> Display.
